title: Flex Que season 7
body:
Curious i know solo/duo will have the soft reset, but
will flex its a new que and a lot off people have done the provisionals will that be reset again ? at the start off season 7 ?

replies.body: [Both queues will have a soft reset on December the 7th when S7 officially starts. ](http://boards.oce.leagueoflegends.com/en/c/gameplay-strategy/z2cArwY8-flex-and-soloduoq?comment=0000)

Riot literally gives me Season 7 for my Birthday.

{{sticker:slayer-jinx-wink}}
